<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٣٩٢ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5638">ابْنُ سَلَامٍ: </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6792">وَكِيعٌ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/644">ابْنِ</a><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٨٤⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أَبِي خَالِدٍ قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3535">ابْنَ أَبِي أَوْفَى </a><span class="special">﵄</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«دَعَا رَسُولُ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> عَلَى الْأَحْزَابِ،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ:</span> اللَّهُمَّ مُنْزِلَ الْكِتَابِ سَرِيعَ الْحِسَابِ، اهْزِمِ الْأَحْزَابَ اهْزِمْهُمْ وَزَلْزِلْهُمْ.»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>